            </svg>
            <h4 class="cc-card-headline">7. Off-Brand U-Shaped Brushes</h4>
            <p class="cc-card-body">Not all U-shaped brushes use medical-grade silicone, true sonic vibration, or come with a dentist endorsement. Material quality matters for something in your child's mouth every day.</p>
            <svg class="cc-tick" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="#2250CE"></circle><path d="M8 12l3 3 5-5" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>
