            <svg class="cc-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#2250CE" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"></path>
            </svg>
            <h4 class="cc-card-headline">8. Mouthwash as a Routine Substitute</h4>
            <p class="cc-card-body">Rinsing supports oral hygiene but doesn't mechanically clean tooth surfaces. It works alongside brushing, not instead of it.</p>
            <svg class="cc-tick" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" fill="#2250CE"></circle><path d="M8 12l3 3 5-5" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg>
